<entry valign="top" align="left">Identify the <emphasis effect="italics">y</emphasis>-intercept.</entry>
<entry valign="top" align="left"><media id="fs-id1167834192127" alt="."><image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_IntAlg_Figure_03_02_014d_img.jpg"/></media></entry>
