<para id="fs-id1167834431107">Graph the line of the equation <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>−</m:mtext><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> using its slope and <emphasis effect="italics">y</emphasis>-intercept.</para>
</problem>
