<solution id="fs-id1167835236599"><media id="fs-id1167835236601" alt="This figure shows the graph of a straight line on the x y-coordinate plane. The x-axis runs from negative 12 to 12. The y-axis runs from negative 12 to 12. The line goes through the points (2, 5) and (5, 4).">
