<solution id="fs-id1167831911528"><media id="fs-id1167831911530" alt="This figure shows the graph of a straight line on the x y-coordinate plane. The x-axis runs from negative 10 to 10. The y-axis runs from negative 10 to 10. The line goes through the points (0, negative 1) and (1, 2).">
