<solution id="fs-id1167831883931"><media id="fs-id1167831883933" alt="This figure shows the graph of a straight line on the x y-coordinate plane. The x-axis runs from negative 10 to 10. The y-axis runs from negative 10 to 10. The line goes through the points (0, 3) and (1, 2).">
