<glossary>
<definition id="fs-id1167827966908">
<term>parallel lines</term><meaning id="fs-id1167834376927">Parallel lines are lines in the same plane that do not intersect.</meaning></definition>
<definition id="fs-id1167834376931">
<term>perpendicular lines</term><meaning id="fs-id1167835418836">Perpendicular lines are lines in the same plane that form a right angle.</meaning></definition></glossary>
